        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Whether it was a new or repeat caller",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The caller's geographic location",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The plumbing company's owner can now see that \"emergency pipe repair\" as a keyword generates calls worth $800 on average, while \"plumbing maintenance\" calls average $150. That insight alone shifts their entire ad budget strategy overnight.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l2",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/how-to-use-whatconverts"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This use case applies to dentists, law firms, HVAC companies, real estate agents — any business where a phone call is a primary lead source. I've written a detailed ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "step-by-step guide on setting up WhatConverts",
            "marks": [
              "l2"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " if you want the full walkthrough.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Use Case 2: Form Submission Tracking for B2B Companies",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "B2B marketers face a different beast. Your leads fill out demo request forms, download whitepapers, or sign up for free trials. The problem? Google Analytics tells you someone submitted a form. It doesn't tell you *who* they are, *what* they want, or *which* campaign brought them.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "WhatConverts captures the full form submission data — name, email, company, custom fields — and ties it directly to the marketing source. No more exporting CSVs and manually cross-referencing.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Picture this: You're a SaaS company running LinkedIn Ads and Google Ads simultaneously. WhatConverts shows you that LinkedIn generates fewer form fills, but those leads convert to paying customers at 3x the rate of Google leads. Without that attribution clarity, you might have slashed the LinkedIn budget. With it, you double down.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l3",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/why-choose-whatconverts"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The platform also scores leads automatically based on the information they provide, so your sales team prioritizes the hottest prospects first. For a deeper dive, check out our article on ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "why choose WhatConverts for lead attribution",
            "marks": [
              "l3"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ".",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
