        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "E-commerce businesses often underestimate how many customers discover them online but convert through a phone call. Think about high-ticket items — furniture, custom jewelry, enterprise software. People want to talk before they buy.",
