      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "WhatConverts attributes that call — and the revenue — back to the original Facebook ad. This level of multi-touch attribution used to require enterprise software costing thousands per month. WhatConverts delivers it at a fraction of the price.",
