        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "One retail client I spoke with discovered that 40% of their phone orders originated from retargeting campaigns they were about to kill. The attribution data literally saved a revenue stream.",
