      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The platform integrates chat conversations into the same lead profile as phone calls and form submissions. So when \"Jane from Acme Corp\" calls on Monday, fills out a form on Wednesday, and chats on Friday, WhatConverts creates one unified lead profile with the full interaction timeline.",
