      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This is massive for businesses with longer sales cycles. Instead of seeing three disconnected touchpoints, your sales team sees one person moving through the funnel. They know Jane first clicked a blog post, then an ad, then reached out directly. That context changes the sales conversation entirely.",
